You can create a new package by dragging one or more files from Windows Explorer(TM) onto the white part of the package tab.

To create a new package from an Outlook(TM) attachment, first drag the attachment to Windows Explorer(TM), then drag the file from Windows Explorer(TM) onto the white part of the package tab.

You can add a document to a package by dragging the file onto the package. If the document is already in the package, thinkParity will ask if you want to replace it.